## Integration with Directory Aggregation

During Phase 2 directory aggregation (`buildDirectoryPrompt()` in `src/generation/prompts/builder.ts`), `detectManifestFiles()` scans the directory for manifest patterns and includes detected files in the AI prompt context. The prompt instructs the AI to recognize these files as dependency declarations and incorporate package information into the `AGENTS.md` directory summary.

This reference document serves as the canonical list for future manifest detection expansion. Adding support for additional languages requires:
1. Updating the `COMMON_MANIFEST_FILES` array in `src/generation/prompts/builder.ts`
2. Marking the language row with `✓` in this table